  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "General Manager",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Summary</strong></p><p>VERIDIAN ENERGY TECH is a Singapore-based energy technology company focused on delivering innovative and sustainable energy solutions. We are seeking an experienced General Manager to lead overall business operations, drive strategic growth, and manage cross-functional teams. This role reports to senior leadership and plays a critical part in shaping the company’s direction, performance, and culture.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Lead and oversee day-to-day business operations to ensure operational excellence and alignment with company objectives</li><li>Develop and implement strategic growth plans that drive measurable business outcomes and enhance market position</li><li>Manage budgets and allocate resources effectively to optimize financial performance and operational efficiency</li><li>Build, lead, and develop a high-performing team by fostering collaboration and aligning departmental goals with company strategy</li><li>Establish and maintain strong relationships with key stakeholders, partners, and clients to support business development and partnership opportunities</li><li>Collaborate with senior leadership to shape company direction, influence decision-making, and promote a culture of innovation and accountability</li></ul><p><strong>Preferred competencies and qualifications</strong></p><ul><li>Master’s degree or Bachelor’s degree in energy systems, engineering, or a closely related field</li><li>Minimum of 10 years of relevant managerial experience with proven leadership in energy, engineering, or technology-driven industries</li><li>Demonstrated strategic thinking skills applied to business growth and operational management</li><li>Proven people management skills in leading diverse teams toward achieving organizational goals</li><li>Strong decision-making abilities in complex and dynamic business environments</li></ul>",
